<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>When using AE songs for non-AE kiting (LDoN, Phase 5 PoTime, AE groups, Farming greens without kiting) the mobs still do move becuase of agro generated by other players.&nbsp; In the&nbsp;acceptable uses of&nbsp;bard AE songs, our damage will be reduced.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I suggest increasing the&nbsp;base damage of our songs by 50%&nbsp;(1.5 multiplier) to account for mob movement.&nbsp; This will still prevent solo AE kiting situations while keeping our DPS constant.</DIV>
